snippet.title: Northend Tower Defense Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
We love tower defense games, we set ourselves to innovate on this genre ( a bit).
Rather than having a straight lines of a puzzle like level, it's more open level now.

Wishlist our game on steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/16...

Discord: https://discord.gg/3sTPnYA627
Patreon : https://cutt.ly/wbOxDLR
Twitter  :  https://cutt.ly/dbOxkGD

Northend Tower Defense game is a ww2 themed inspired tower defense where you hold the line and defend your commander. You have different types of units, upgrades, and abilities, Experiment with builds in a thrilling fight.
